# soft-check-mixed.tflw — DEMO-FAIL FIXTURE (PLAN M1.5): two passing and two failing soft
# `check`s in one test — a soft check (unlike `expect`) doesn't fail fast, so all 4 checks run and
# each shows as its own pass/fail row in the report.
#
# Run explicitly (dot-directory, invisible to a bare `tflw run`/`tflw check`):
#   npx tflw run tests/.demo-fail/*.tflw --tag demofail

@demofail @softmixed
test "two passing and two failing soft checks in one test"
  api GET /health
  check status equals 200
  check status equals 999
  check body.status equals "OK"
  check body.status equals "NOPE"
